link: Index entries for sequences that are permutations of the natural numbers
xref: A072657(n) = A057163(A072659(n)). A072660 gives the size of the corresponding parenthesizations, i.e. A072660(n) = A029837(A014486(A072657(n))+1)/2 [A029837(n+1) gives the binary width of n].
